Re: bitcoin 0.3 win64 - broken access to APPDATA if non-latin characters in
username

Bitcointalk

2010-07-08 18:24:19 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Thanks for finding that.  We switched from ANSI in 0.2 to UTF-8 in
   version 0.3, so it must be related to that.
   Just to confirm, if you log in with the non-latin character username,
   not having an appdata/Bitcoin directory yet, and run Bitcoin and let it
   create the database from scratch, does it work or not?
